== 重啟 ==
2019年7月，華納宣佈製作《摩登原始人》重啟系列，由[[伊莉莎白·班克絲|伊莉莎白·班克絲]]和她的影視製作公司負責開發<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/the-flintstones-animated-series-reboot-warner-bros-animation-elizabeth-banks-1202645055/|title=‘The Flintstones’ Animated Series Reboot In Works At Warner Bros. With Elizabeth Banks Producing|website=Deadline|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2019-07-11|language=en-US|access-date=2019-07-12|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225165605/https://deadline.com/2019/07/the-flintstones-animated-series-reboot-warner-bros-animation-elizabeth-banks-1202645055/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

